name: Pizza
details: Delicious pizza topped with tomato sauce, cheese, and your choice of toppings. Baked to perfection in a wood-fired oven.

name: Burger
details: Classic beef patty, lettuce, tomato, cheese, and special sauce in a soft bun. Served with crispy fries.

name: Taco
details: Soft corn tortillas filled with seasoned ground beef, lettuce, cheese, and salsa. A taste of Mexico in every bite.

name: Pad Thai
details: Stir-fried rice noodles with shrimp, tofu, peanuts, and tamarind sauce. A harmonious blend of sweet, sour, and spicy flavors.

name: Pasta
details: Al dente pasta served with a rich and creamy Alfredo sauce, garnished with parmesan cheese and parsley.

name: Ramen
details: Steaming bowl of ramen with tender slices of pork, boiled egg, and savory broth. A hearty and comforting dish.

name: Curry
details: Spicy and aromatic curry with tender chicken, served with naan bread and rice. A taste of India on your plate.

name: Tiramisu
details: A classic Italian dessert made with layers of coffee-soaked ladyfingers and mascarpone cheese, dusted with cocoa powder.

name: Sushi Rolls
details: Exquisite sushi rolls featuring a variety of fish and seafood, expertly crafted by our sushi chef.

name: Lobster Bisque
details: Creamy and indulgent lobster bisque, made with fresh lobster meat, brandy, and a touch of cream. Served with crusty bread.
